title: [FasterTransformer] Update FasterTransformer and add performance info logger
body:
<!-- Demo: https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleNLP/pull/26 -->
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
Others

### PR changes
<!-- One of [ Models | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
Others

### Description
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
[FasterTransformer] Update FasterTransformer and add performance info logger. 

The detail performance info will be printed in this PR later. Average latency for 3003 sentences in `en-de` Translation. 

| hyper params | fp32(in ms/batch) | fp16(in ms/batch) | Original(in ms/batch) | speedup(compare with fp32) |
|--|--|--|--|--|
| batch_size: 1, beam_size: 1 | 36.6575 | 41.9541 | 1288.0803 | 35.1382 |
| batch_size: 1, beam_size: 4 | 49.5412 | 46.2929 | 1232.0821 | 24.87 |
| batch_size: 8, beam_size: 1 | 67.2444 | 64.3771 | 1997.2295 | 29.70 |
| batch_size: 8, beam_size: 4 | 75.6515 | 66.5741 | 2135.4212 | 28.23 |
| batch_size: 32, beam_size: 1 | 97.9693 | 84.9347 | 2633.8843 | 26.88 |
| batch_size: 32, beam_size: 4 | 184.9824 | 133.9078 | 2606.9408 | 14.09 |
| batch_size: 64, beam_size: 1 | 152.0229 | 122.5850 | 2881.6411 | 18.96 |
| batch_size: 64, beam_size: 4 | 347.8825 | 218.8199 | 3391.2002 | 9.75 |

**Note**:
* `fp16` means using `fp16` to calculate `decoding` while using `fp32` to calculate `encoder`. Hence, there is a `paddle.cast` casting the output of `encoder` to `fp16`, which may lead to performance drop. 
* The larger `batch_size`/`beam_size`, the less speedup. Since with the increasing number of `batch_size`/`beam_size`, the bottleneck of performance is no longer launching an op/kernel, but the computing in an op/kernel, which cannot be solved by fusion.

鉴于目前 paddle 中的 get_path_from_url 接口在被多卡多进程调用时各进程并非严格意义上的竞争关系，实际上写死了只有某个确定的进程会去下载这个数据 https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/Paddle/blob/develop/python/paddle/utils/download.py#L152 ，这里也可以先不考虑文件锁，只让这个确定的进程去get_data并在完成后touch一个类似squad.done的文件，其他进程都在wait，wait时循环检测这个文件是否存在，存在的话就认为数据获取完成结束wait。这些逻辑可以加在get_data https://github.com/PaddlePaddle/PaddleNLP/blob/develop/paddlenlp/datasets/dataset.py#L508 前后

title: Add tiny bert model
body:
### PR types
<!-- One of [ New features | Bug fixes | Function optimization | Performance optimization | Breaking changes | Others ] -->
New features
### PR changes
<!-- One of [ Models | APIs | Docs | Others ] -->
APIs
### Describe
<!-- Describe what this PR does -->
- 重新定义了`MultiHeadAttention`,  `TransformerEncoderLayer`, `TransformerEncoder`的`forward`函数（为了定义用于蒸馏的`TinyBertModel`，`TinyBertModel`需要拿到每一层的attention_scores和每一层`TransformerEncoder`的输出
- 增加3个class: `TinyBertModel`,  `TinyBertForPretraining`,  `TinyBertForSequenceClassification`
- 以`TinyBertForSequenceClassification`为例，在fp64下，对齐和竞品的logits、及中间输出attention_output, sequence_output：
a.6l_768_dim下结果均能对齐；
b.6l_768_dim_v2下输出的 logits能对齐，中间输出部分少数tensor的最大相对diff数量级在n*1e-7；
c.4l_312d和4l_312d_v2下输出的logits能对齐，中间输出部分最大相对误差常是1e-2，1e-3的n倍(n:1-9)
d.不过，对于上面说的中间结果不符合预期的相对误差(数量级1e-2，1e-3），常发生在很小的数上（<1e-6)，且原因是【除以math.sqrt运算】放大了误差；
- 增加`to_distill`函数，绑定在带有transformer layer的layer子类对象上，调用之后可以获取中间transformer层的输出、attention matrix，以及embedding的输出
